Carlo_Paalam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlo_Paalam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paalam inched closer to a Paris Games berth as he beat Turkmenistan's Shukur Ovezov in the round of 32 of the men's 57kg class in the second World Qualification Tournament in Bangkok, Thailand, on Tuesday, May 28.\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 455, \"end\": 467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkmenistan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999695857605263, \"rank\": 3.041515834663353e-05, \"text\": \"Turkmenistan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkmenistan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkmenistan_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 575, \"end\": 582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\", \"score\": 0.9999999956239662, \"rank\": 4.365708599287217e-09, \"text\": \"Bangkok\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\"}, {\"begin\": 584, \"end\": 592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9607093679558261, \"rank\": 0.04084793919313404, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Winning via unanimous decision, Paalam earned identical scores of 30-27 from the five judges to move within three victories of joining fellow boxersEumir Marcial,Nesthy Petecio, andAira Villegasin the Olympic cast.\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 777, \"end\": 791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nesthy_Petecio\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nesthy Petecio\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nesthy_Petecio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nesthy_Petecio\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am happy that I am now able to move properly,\\\" said Paalam in Filipino.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will work harder in my next fights.\\\"\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a sweet payback for Paalam after he lost to Ovezov in the first World Qualification Tournament in Busto Arsizio, Italy, in March as hesurrenderedin the second round of their last 16 bout due to a shoulder injury.\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 1166, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1052, \"end\": 1065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Busto_Arsizio\", \"score\": 0.9999997922532418, \"rank\": 2.0774474536095948e-07, \"text\": \"Busto Arsizio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Busto_Arsizio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Busto_Arsizio\"}, {\"begin\": 1067, \"end\": 1072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9654059739053636, \"rank\": 0.035426843308139576, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paalam sustained the injury in his previous fight and opted to throw in the towel against Ovezov to avoid the \\\"risk of further damage.\\\"\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That decision has worked wonders for the Tokyo Games silver medalist, who has rediscovered his form as he won his first two bouts in Bangkok via unanimous decision, the first comingagainst Greece's Alexei Lagkazasvili.\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1438, \"end\": 1445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\", \"score\": 0.9999999956239662, \"rank\": 4.365708599287217e-09